quran[21]{c,v,t}:
  26,40,"Khaundi khunyala okhuloonda abalosi nikali mbu nibo nibalashila.”"
  26,41,"Kho mana abalosi shingala boola, nibaboolela Firauni mbu: “Koo, khulanyoola omurungo nikaba mbu nefwe khushila?”"
  26,42,"Naboola mbu: “Eeh, ne khandi mwitsa okhuba mubalia abalarebwa hambi.”"
  26,43,"Musa nababoolela mbu: “Sukune ebiamwenya okhusukuna.”"
  26,44,"Nibasukuna emikoye chiabu nende tsindabushi tsiabu, ne nibaboola mbu: “Khumaani ka Firauni efwe sa toto nefwe khulashila.”"
  26,45,"Mana Musa nasukuna indabushi yiyie, mana niimilaa bioosi biabachikhanga."
  26,46,"Awo abalosi nibakwa hasi, nibara hasi obweni bwabu (nibasujuda)."
  26,47,"Nibaboola mbu: “Khusuubile Nyasaye Omulesi webiloonje bioosi."
  26,48,"Nyasaye Omulesi wa Musa nende Haruni.”"
  26,49,"(Firauni) naboola mbu: “Mumusuubile neshili okhubasubula. Toto ye niye Omukhongo wenyu owabechesia obulosi. Kho, mwitsa okhulola. Nditsa toto okhuteta emikhono chienyu nende ebilenje bienyu buchikha, ne toto nditsa okhubabamba mwesi.”"
  26,50,"Nibaboola mbu: “Obubii bubulaho tawe. Toto efwe khwitsa okhukalukha khu Nyasaye wefu Omulesi."
  26,51,"Toto efwe khusuubile mbu Nyasaye wefu Omulesi alakhuleshela tsimbi tsiefu shichila efwe khubeele bokhuranjilila okhusuubila.”"
  26,52,"Ne nikhufimbulila Musa mbu: “Rula nende abandu banje ebise bieshilo, toto enywe mwitsa okhulondwakho.”"
  26,53,"Mana Firauni naruma abakhung’asinjia abandu mumatokho."
  26,54,""Toto bano ni omukanda omutiti."
  26,55,"Nabo toto bakhusinyisinjia muno."
  26,56,"Nafu toto khuli abanji, ne khukholele koosi kookhukhula efwe khubashile.”"
  26,57,"Mana nikhubarusia mumikunda nende tsisebele."
  26,58,"Nende emiandu emisirosiro nende habundu andayi."
  26,59,"Ne endio, mana nikhuchelamia ebio Abana ba Israili."
  26,60,"Mana olwa eliuba liarula itsuli, nibabalondakhwo."